#

Minestrone Soup

45 min
$10
220 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVeganGluten-Free Option

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main

Tags:

SoupItalianHealthyComfort Food

Description

A hearty and healthy Italian vegetable soup brimming with beans, pasta, and vibrant veggies.

Ingredients

  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • onion: 1, diced
  • carrot: 2, diced
  • celery: 2 stalks, diced
  • garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • zucchini: 1, diced
  • green beans: 1 cup, chopped
  • canned diced tomatoes: 1 can (14.5 oz)
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • canned cannellini beans: 1 can (15 oz), drained and rinsed
  • pasta (small shapes): 1 cup
  • italian seasoning: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • fresh basil (optional): for garnish
